# Cursor — iran-market-terminal

PRIMARY DOC: docs/AGENT_PLAYBOOK.md  (read fully at session start)

MANDATORY every session / before any edit:
  git fetch origin && git checkout main && git pull --ff-only origin main

Stack:
  docker compose up -d --build
  Postgres only (Alembic migrations auto on start)
  If build DNS fails: ./scripts/prepare-offline-build.sh

Also: AGENTS.md, docs/DATABASE.md, README.md
Bump APP_VERSION on product changes.
